next week at @aiDotEngineer, we are joining @togethercompute for a conversation on what goes into running agents at scale.

@olive_jy_song, Research Lead, RL at MiniMax, and
@realDanFu, VP of Kernels at Together AI, will walk through both sides of M3: the training decisions behind long-context reasoning and tool use, and the infrastructure work needed to serve agentic workloads in production.  

Wed July 1, 2:50 PM PDT 
Room 2016, Track 9 
Catch you there!
